full_text:
Hi Juli,

Thanks! Lots of food for thought here.

I do not know for sure exactly who is communicating with us via Frank&#39;s 
boxes or what their intents are. This is a new mystery opened up by our 
newer technology. It interested me that they make predictions that don&#39;t 
happen, or in some cases seem to be lying.

About 10-15 years ago quite a few people (myself included) built what we 
call &quot;Barkhausen effect detectors&quot;. You can see the details at the 
website below.  The Barkhausen detector starts about 1/3 of the way down 
the page and goes to the bottom. A few of the parts are VERY difficult to 
come by. The inventor sent me a couple extra pieces of his material used 
to make the coil core.

http://amasci.com/freenrg/bark.html

Most of us picked up voices on these things at one time or another.  Alas, 
neither I nor anyone else recorded them. We had no idea where the voices 
were coming from.  Some people felt they were extraterrestrials.  It 
seemed odd that they spoke in Earth languages and usually the language of 
the user, though.

I still have the device around somewhere and might dig it out one of 
these days (I think it&#39;s in the attic) and do some more experimentation 
with it.

Zack

On Thu, 15 Nov 2007, juli velazquez wrote:

&gt; Hey Zack:
&gt;                    I have had the schematics for about 2 years now, but I am not mechanical inclined myself to build one.  I have strong convictions regarding the boxes, having been up close and personal (shall we say) on several different occasions.  I have analyzed EVP from many locations and still strongly believe that the box does not work for everyone.  I believe that your intentions are good giving our conversations in the past and wish you the very best with assembly.
&gt;
&gt;  See, I believe that the guilds know what your intentions are, and the sincerity behind your work and come through to those who have their best interest at heart.  I know that you probably think I am crazy, but in viewing some who currently posses the devices and having changed their path for their own agenda, its not going to be what they in vision it to be.  I think they could open Pandora Box and the world in which they know it will come crashing down upon their own accord.
&gt;
&gt;  I know the other side knows, and will help those in furthering their studies as they see fit.  I can only say, that the respect I have for the boxes and Frank will always remain, and I can lay my head upon my pillow at night with my integrity in take.  When I should have a box, I will know, and until then, I have the pleasure to listen and read everyones data and studies!
&gt;
&gt;  Juli
